  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the study is to compare the CACS obtained from standard dose CT to the CACS
      obtained from ultra-low-dose scans. Additionally, the usefulness of ultra-low-dose CT for AC
      of myocardial perfusion SPECT will be assessed.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
